{"tid":424810,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"屌嬲，中秋節馮型型同男友晒月光","createTime":"2017-10-05T06:11:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T08:43:12.000Z","uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"59240eb56033b4c7827dea07d2c5f2645351fe62","tid":424810,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T06:11:35.000Z","msg":"[quote]<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171004/photo/bkn-20171004002030621-1004_00862_001_01p.jpg?20171004060421\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171004%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171004002030621-1004_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20171004060421&h=8945da0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n盈盈之前素顏畀人笑「無眉娘」，紋咗眉其實都未至於唔認得啫！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n無綫晚上在將軍澳電視城舉行《big big channel 失驚無神賀中秋》，馮盈盈、劉穎鏇與一班KOL齊齊進行《＃後生仔傾吓偈》網上直播環節。馮盈盈被問到與男友怎樣慶祝中秋﹖她笑說：「真係好彩，近排拍劇又要主持節目會比較忙，但中秋竟然放假，首先會陪屋企人，食完飯諗住同佢去沙灘睇月光食月餅。（唔怕畀人認到﹖）我已經發現咗一個秘技，就係唔化妝出街，我觀察到一個現象，唔化妝啲人係認唔到我，化咗妝啲人先認到嘅，所以冇擔心唔方便畀人認到。（有冇檢討吓啲人認唔到你﹖）都值得自豪㗎，哈哈。不過，唔化妝我會戴眼鏡，氣質即刻唔同咗，唔化妝有種清純、純樸嘅感覺，可塑性好高，哈哈。」<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171004/photo/bkn-20171004002030621-1004_00862_001_02b.jpg?20171004060421\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171004%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171004002030621-1004_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20171004060421&h=3dbf2680&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n盈盈話近排好忙，不過中秋有假放！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171004/photo/bkn-20171004002030621-1004_00862_001_03b.jpg?20171004060421\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171004%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171004002030621-1004_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20171004060421&h=bc9a43a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n左起：馮盈盈、劉穎鏇、湯洛雯及高海寧。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171004/photo/bkn-20171004002030621-1004_00862_001_04b.jpg?20171004060421\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171004%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171004002030621-1004_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20171004060421&h=8d8274d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n中秋會同男友去沙灘睇月光食月餅。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171004/photo/bkn-20171004002030621-1004_00862_001_05b.jpg?20171004060421\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171004%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171004002030621-1004_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20171004060421&h=0ca711f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n話唔怕畀人認出，因為自己素顏判若兩人！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171004/photo/bkn-20171004002030621-1004_00862_001_06b.jpg?20171004060421\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171004%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171004002030621-1004_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20171004060421&h=54b9b8df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n仲話覺得好係值得自豪！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171004/photo/bkn-20171004002030621-1004_00862_001_07b.jpg?20171004060421\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171004%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171004002030621-1004_00862_001_07b.jpg%3F20171004060421&h=d59cddf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n盈盈話自己唔化妝有種清純、純樸嘅感覺。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171004/photo/bkn-20171004002030621-1004_00862_001_08b.jpg?20171004060421\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171004%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171004002030621-1004_00862_001_08b.jpg%3F20171004060421&h=3689d631&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n佢講嘢真係好率真可愛呀！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171004/photo/bkn-20171004002030621-1004_00862_001_09b.jpg?20171004060421\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171004%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171004002030621-1004_00862_001_09b.jpg%3F20171004060421&h=b7acb316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n盈盈素顏都唔係佢講得咁差啫！（資料圖片）"},{"pid":"750cb00b2db9240ac27cd7fda2a47c74aceca90c","tid":424810,"uid":87625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T06:13:00.000Z","msg":"你唔屌 我屌"},{"pid":"3a56f2fc7b0999aa6be8dd772b6874ea6681b682","tid":424810,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T06:13:30.000Z","msg":"隻腳咁多一點點"},{"pid":"a17bf89e4912540c0fe3cfabda2cf2a8bc088e6d","tid":424810,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T08:43:12.000Z","msg":"9up"}]}